name: ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴇᴠᴇɴᴛᴇᴇɴᴛʜ ᴏɴᴇ
description:
I use squares, circles and triangles as simple compositional elements in some of my work. This piece was made on Ilford black and white photographic paper with developer and fixer. The developer was a homemade mixture of coffee, vitamin C and washing soda. Inks and varnishes were added.

NFT is 8K.
